  "method": [
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "For the oats, combine all the oat ingredients in a mixing bowl and whisk together until well combined. Pour into an airtight container and refrigerate overnight."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "For the yoghurt topping, add the yoghurt to a clean mixing bowl with the honey and almond milk. Whisk vigorously for about 2 mins until the mixture becomes shiny and slightly aerated. Pour into a separate airtight container and refrigerate overnight. The oats will keep for 4 days."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "In the morning, serve up a portion of the oats into a bowl and top with the yoghurt. Finish with toppings of your choice: we love a scattering of crunchy nut cornflakes; a drizzle of honey and some grated frozen strawberries; or a sprinkling of cinnamon, sliced banana and a handful of granola."
    }
